object.script:
function onTick() fuel = input.getNumber(8) battery = input.getNumber(9) temperature = input.getNumber(14) end
function onDraw() screen.setColor (0,100,0)
screen.drawText(1,5,"BAT") if battery < property.getNumber("Battery level warning") then screen.setColor (100,0,0) end screen.drawTextBox(17,5,15,5,string.format("%.1f",battery),0,0) screen.setColor (0,100,0)
screen.drawText(1,13,"FUL") if fuel < property.getNumber("Fuel level warning") then screen.setColor (100,0,0) end screen.drawTextBox(17,13,15,5,math.floor(fuel),0,0) screen.setColor (0,100,0)
screen.drawText(1,21,"TMP") if temperature > property.getNumber("Temperature level warning") then screen.setColor (100,0,0) end screen.drawTextBox(17,21,15,5,math.floor(temperature),0,0) screen.setColor (0,100,0)
end

function onTick() speed = input.getNumber(1) altitude = input.getNumber(2) pitch = -input.getNumber(3) roll = -input.getNumber(4) vertical = input.getNumber(5) angular = input.getNumber(6) heading = math.floor(math.fmod((360-input.getNumber(7)*360),360)) fuel = input.getNumber(8) battery = input.getNumber(9)
gyrocopter = input.getBool(19) slow = input.getBool(3)
end
function onDraw() width = screen.getWidth() width2 = width/2 width4 = width/4 height = screen.getHeight() height2 = height/2 height4 = height/4 screen.setColor (0,100,0)
screen.drawLine(width2, 0, width2, 2) screen.drawLine(0, 0, 0, 2) screen.drawLine(width-1, 0, width-1, 2) screen.drawLine(width4, 0, width4, 2) screen.drawLine(width*3/4, 0, width*3/4, 2) screen.drawLine(width*6/10, 0, width*6/10, 2) screen.drawLine(width*4/10, 0, width*4/10, 2) screen.drawRectF(width2, 0, angular*120, 1)
screen.drawLine(width-2, 0, width, 0) screen.drawLine(width-2, height-1, width, height-1) screen.drawLine(width-2, height2, width, height2) screen.drawLine(width-2, height*6/10, width, height*6/10) screen.drawLine(width-2, height*4/10, width, height*4/10) screen.drawLine(width-2, height4, width, height4) screen.drawLine(width-2, height*3/4, width, height*3/4) screen.drawRectF(width-1, height2, width, -150*vertical)
screen.drawLine(width2-2, height*3/4-4, width2+3, height*3/4-4) screen.drawLine(width2-2, height4-4, width2+3, height4-4) screen.drawLine(width2-1, height*4/10-4, width2+2, height*4/10-4) screen.drawLine(width2-1, height*6/10-4, width2+2, height*6/10-4) screen.drawLine(width2, height*3/4-4, width2, -height*pitch+height2-4) screen.drawLine(width2-1, -height*pitch+height2-4, width2+2, -height*pitch+height2-4)
screen.drawLine(width2-15*math.cos(2*roll*math.pi), height2+15*math.sin(2*roll*math.pi)-4, width2+15*math.cos(2*roll*math.pi), height2-15*math.sin(2*roll*math.pi)-4) screen.drawLine(width2+15, height2-4, width2+20, height2-4) screen.drawLine(width2-15, height2-4, width2-20, height2-4) screen.drawLine(width2+13, height2-9-4, width2+14, height2-9-4) screen.drawLine(width2-13, height2-9-4, width2-14, height2-9-4) screen.drawLine(width2+13, height2+9-4, width2+14, height2+9-4) screen.drawLine(width2-13, height2+9-4, width2-14, height2+9-4)
screen.drawTextBox(1,3,width,7,heading,0,0) screen.drawTextBox(0,48,width,7,"SPD:"..math.floor(3.6*speed).." kph",0,0) screen.drawTextBox(0,56,width,7,"ALT:"..math.floor(altitude).." m",0,0)
if gyrocopter and not slow then screen.drawTriangleF(width2-18, height4-6, width2-9, height4-6, width2-14, height4-11)
end if slow then screen.drawTriangleF(width2+19, height4-12, width2+9, height4-12, width2+14, height4-6) end
screen.setColor (200,0,0) if fuel < property.getNumber ("Fuel level warning") then screen.drawTextBox(0,14,width,7,"FUEL", 0, 0) elseif battery < property.getNumber("Battery level warning") then screen.drawTextBox(0,14,width,7,"BATTERY", 0, 0) end
end

freqLow = 500 freqHigh = 600
maxDelay = 7 delay = maxDelay
RFreq = freqLow TFreq = freqLow
first = true firstFirst = true
callsign = string.sub(string.upper(property.getText("Callsign")), 1, 8)
function onTick()
if first then if firstFirst then firstFirst = false output.setNumber(14, TFreq)
for i = 1, #callsign do output.setNumber(i + 4, string.byte(callsign, i)) end
elseif delay <= 0 then
if input.getBool(1) then TFreq = TFreq + 1 output.setNumber(14, TFreq) delay = maxDelay else first = false output.setNumber(13, TFreq) end
end delay = delay - 1 else
output.setNumber(1, input.getNumber(12)) --gpsX output.setNumber(2, input.getNumber(13)) --gpsY output.setNumber(3, input.getNumber(2)) --altitude output.setNumber(4, input.getNumber(1)) --seed
output.setBool(1, true)
RFreq = RFreq + 1 if RFreq > freqHigh then RFreq = freqLow end
output.setNumber(14, RFreq)
correctFreq = RFreq - 5 if correctFreq < freqLow then correctFreq = correctFreq + (freqHigh - freqLow) + 1 end
if input.getBool(1) and correctFreq == TFreq then
first = true firstFirst = true
delay = maxDelay
TFreq = freqLow + 10 + math.floor(gpsX % 10) end end end

function onTick() transponderF = input.getNumber(1) radioF = input.getNumber(2) transponder = input.getBool(1) harness1 = input.getBool(2) harness2 = input.getBool(3) end
function onDraw() screen.setColor(0, 100, 0)
screen.drawText(1,5,"TRN") if transponder then screen.drawTextBox(17,5,15,5,string.format("%.0f",transponderF),0,0) else screen.drawTextBox(17,5,15,5,"---",0,0) end
screen.drawText(1,13,"RAD") screen.drawTextBox(17,13,15,5,string.format("%.0f",radioF),0,0)
screen.drawText(1,21,"HAR")
if harness1 then screen.drawRectF(18,21,5,6) else screen.drawRect(18,21,4,5) end if harness2 then screen.drawRectF(25,21,5,6) else screen.drawRect(25,21,4,5) end
end

zoom = 1 speed = 0.1 reset = true switch = false
function inRect(x, y, rectx, recty, rectw, recth) return x>rectx and y>recty and x<rectw+rectx and y<recth+recty end
function drawPointer(x,y,s,r) a = 30*math.pi/360 x = x+s/2*math.sin(r) y = y-s/2*math.cos(r) screen.drawTriangleF(x,y, x-s*math.sin(r+a), y+s*math.cos(r+a), x-s*math.sin(r-a), y+s*math.cos(r-a)) end
function onTick() touchX = input.getNumber(3) touchY = input.getNumber(4) compass = -math.pi*2*input.getNumber(7) gpsX = input.getNumber(8) gpsY = input.getNumber(9) pressedPulse=input.getBool(1) and not pressed pressed=input.getBool(1)
end
function onDraw() width = screen.getWidth() height = screen.getHeight() screen.setMapColorOcean(10, 10, 10) screen.setMapColorShallows(20, 20, 20) screen.setMapColorLand(40, 40, 40) screen.setMapColorGrass(50, 50, 50) screen.setMapColorSand(50, 50, 50) screen.setMapColorSnow(50, 50, 50)
if reset then zoom = 1 currentX = gpsX currentY = gpsY targetX = gpsX targetY = gpsY end
currentX = currentX*(1-speed)+targetX*speed currentY = currentY*(1-speed)+targetY*speed selfX, selfY = map.mapToScreen(currentX, currentY, zoom, width, height, gpsX, gpsY)
if switch then screen.setColor(0,50,0) screen.drawLine(width/2,height/2,width/2+1,height/2)
screen.drawRect(30, 0, 33, 8) screen.drawRectF(0, 0, 30, 9) screen.drawTextBox(30, 1, 33, 7, "MAP", 0, 0)
screen.setColor(0,0,0,100) screen.drawTextBox(0, 1, 30, 7, "CAM", 0, 0) else screen.drawMap(currentX, currentY, zoom)
screen.setColor(0,100,0) screen.drawLine(width/2,height/2,width/2+1,height/2) drawPointer(selfX, selfY, 10, compass)
screen.setColor(0,255,0,50) screen.drawLine(0, 9, 0, height-2) screen.drawLine(0, height-1, width-2, height-1) screen.drawLine(width-1, height-1, width-1, 8) screen.drawRect(0, 0, 31, 8) screen.drawTextBox(0, 1, 31, 7, "CAM", 0, 0) screen.drawRectF(32, 0, 32, 9)
screen.setColor(0,0,0,150) screen.drawText(36, 2, "R") screen.drawText(46, 2, "+") screen.drawText(56, 2, "-") end
if pressed and not switch then screen.setColor(200,200,200) if inRect(touchX, touchY, 0, 0, 31, 10) then switch = true elseif inRect(touchX, touchY, 30, 0, 13, 10) then reset = true screen.drawText(36, 2, "R") elseif inRect(touchX, touchY, 42, 0, 11, 10) then zoom = math.max(0.5, (zoom-0.1)) reset = false screen.drawText(46, 2, "+") elseif inRect(touchX, touchY, 52, 0, 12, 10) then zoom = math.min(20, (zoom+0.1)) reset = false screen.drawText(56, 2, "-") elseif pressedPulse then targetX, targetY = map.screenToMap(currentX, currentY, zoom, width, height, touchX, touchY) reset = false end elseif not pressed and inRect(touchX, touchY, 30, 0, 33, 10) then switch = false end
end
